# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# CSP NOTE: unsafe-inline and unsafe-eval are currently required
# because all page scripts are inline <script> blocks and some
# libraries (Tailwind CSS JIT, Alpine.js) use eval().
#
# Migration plan:
#   1. Extract inline scripts to external .js files
#   2. Add nonce-based CSP for remaining inline scripts
#   3. Replace eval-dependent libraries (Tailwind → build step)
#   4. Remove unsafe-inline and unsafe-eval once steps 1-3 done
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

